  "texts": [
    "Further, we selected the top K single drug candidates.",
    "The top K single drug candidates were used to construct ∑ i=n i=2 C i K drug combinations for optimisation.",
    "K was chosen to select complementary drugs as much as possible (in terms of the coverage of proteins they could target) while accounting for the combinatorial cost.",
    "The intuition was that the marginal benefit of including more drugs to cover more drug targets would decrease at a certain point.",
    "Specifically, the optimal K was determined by a drug-target coverage curve, an increasing function characterizing the trade-off relationship between the benefit and the cost."
  ],
